		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />MEKA has a debugger, but I don't know how hacker-friendly it is.  It seems more gamer-friendly than anything.<br /><br />MESS supports the SMS and has a pretty thorough debugger/logger, IIRC.

		

		</td>
